      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "Bad, bad, bad",
      "review_description": "Tried it on oculus go. The graphics is 1980 style. The software stuck several times - had to shut it down and restart. Controls with Oculus controller are very bad and probably incomplete. The speed didn't exceed 15mph first - didn't know how to switch gears. After many tries suddenly it started to switch gears automatically. Then I was able to fire a missile - since then never again. There is no manual - no explanation - the tutorial is a joke. Very funny - they force you to watch an advertisement for the very same bad game you just downloaded... how stupid is that?",
